Subject: mvtnorm package

Hi Torsten,

It's a very minor point regarding the documentation of mvtnorm.  In
?dmvt you refer to sigma as the 'covariance matrix'.  I think it is
better to refer to this as the 'scale matrix', because the covariance is
(df / (df - 2)) * sigma.

Best wishes, Jonathan.

